START
|
|-- Is the PC powering on?
|-- NO → Check power cable → Test outlet → Try a different PSU → END
|-- YES


|-- Is the system booting to OS?
|-- NO → Check boot device → Run startup repair → Check drive health → END
|-- YES


|-- Is the PC running slow?
|-- YES → Check Task Manager → Remove startup apps → Run virus scan → Check disk space → END
|-- NO


|-- Is there a network issue?
|-- YES → Restart router → Check IP config → Test DNS → Reset network → END
|-- NO


|-- Is there a software/app issue?
|-- YES → Restart app → Update app → Reinstall → Check event viewer → END
|-- NO


END